ActNational Defence Act
SubjectDesignation of Judges as Judges of the Court Martial Appeal Court of Canada
PrecisOrder designating four judges as Judges of the Court Martial Appeal Court of Canada, as follows: 1. The Honourable Alexandre Deschênes, Court of Appeal of New Brunswick 2. The Honourable J. Douglas Cunningham, Superior Court of Justice in and for the Province of Ontario 3. The Honourable Guy Cournoyer, Superior Court of Québec 4. The Honourable Douglas N. Abra, Court of Queen's Bench for Manitoba
